  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      All participants will be randomized at elective cesarean section to either irrigation with
      500 to 1000 ml of warm normal saline after closure of visceral peritoneum or non irrigation
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      All participants will be randomized at elective cesarean section to either irrigation with
      500 to 1000 ml of warm normal saline after closure of visceral peritoneum or non irrigation
      during the procedure of elective lower segment cesarean section
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
